  <summary date="2022-03-24T19:18:33Z" status="Introduced in House">Safer Heat Act of 2022

This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to establish safety standards for portable heating devices, including a requirement that a device shuts off at a threshold determined hazardous by the commission. The commission is authorized to enforce these standards.</summary>
